Package edu.monash.fit2099.vehicles

package edu.monash.fit2099.vehicles
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    Sedan
    creates a vehicle object of sedan type, sedan is an extension of the vehicle class so its attributes consists of everything in the vehicle class, with the addition of the attribute seats
    Truck
    creates a vehicle object of truck type, truck is an extension of the vehicle class so its attributes consists of everything in the vehicle class, with the addition of the attribute capacity and wheels
    Vehicle
    Vehicle class, this is where the vehicle object is made it has the attributes: maker: a user inputted string to tell the vehicle's maker model: a user inputted string to tell the vehicle's model vehicleID: a random generated ID attached to every vehicle object instanceofBidHashmap: the hashmap of bids attached to every vehicle
